Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\blur0.7\bord0\pos(347.43,293)}Animation Production: Studio Pierrot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, a specialist rider?{note: I assume this is 専属 ? - as he'd be given a specialist racing contract?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:00:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called the \NHagiwara Racing Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The races they arrange make us\N look like amateurs in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And those Hagiwara guys saw your performance at\N the four-hour race and want you all to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really do want to get into the racing scene, I don't think this is a bad offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean my\N dream will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, you'll need to get \Npromoted to B-class before year's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you pull out all the\N stops in the remaining races,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they can recommend you \Nget promoted to B-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more, \NHideo "Pops" Yoshimura... {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pops_Yoshimura}{using his full name for clarity}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this time... my\N dream's finally coming true...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoyo! You seen \Nmy Katana keys? {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzuki_Katana}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they in \Nthe usual place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would I be askin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's strange,\N I always leave them around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi, can't you \Njust skip this morning?{calling him brother sounds weird in Eng imo}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I could...{this is how I *feel* the JP  - let's just assume this is right}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, if you can't find something before \Ngoing out, it's God's way of telling you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening \Nto me, Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, that's \Njus' a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are. Must've \Ndropped them 'round back. {not sure what's this about - pushed to the opposite side}{反対側に落ちた w/ an accent?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I'll see you later.{changed}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothin' to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the color \Nof that sky one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain pass \Nsure is great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's somethin' else, alright. {not sure how a touge can be "interesting; fascinating; intriguing; enthralling"}{Ahem, I'll have you know...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, this is it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last time you'll \Never race me on the pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Startin' today, \Nthis highway racer's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joining the big leagues.{I'm just not gonna shoehorn in the word major}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks out of it.\N What's gotten into him?{ just 調子が狂う ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and see you 'round, winding \Nroads of the mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a handshake, Beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But what for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one weird dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go? We can \Ntake it nice and easy.{just didn't wanna put "niiiice and easy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awfully lively for\N some rich, little upstart! {TLC, only hear "ondore koso me ga gingin ya kono tsukaza}{added in what I hear - last word seems to be from 使わざる者?}{that should do though, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat you \Non the pass this time! { sounds like 俺一遍峠道お前に勝ちたいんだよ to me}{I'm also under the impression Gun still can't overtake him}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In your dreams! {guess, TLC, maybe "perfect/great"}{this just せこい  --> せこっ ?}{I do like current line as it is thoug}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just pass those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so fast! {can't tell if Perevo is messing with me atm lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You tryin' ta get \Nyourself killed, dipshit?! {watch me pretend Perevo's note wasn't here in the first place}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That got the blood flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too narrow! {semai?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh{\fscx200}—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone wiped out! {ye, I hear 転倒 too}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it! { 噛ませる ?  - as in he goes for the (more dangerous) inside gap}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
